story: Once upon a time, in The Eyrie there was a murderer whose name was Jon Snow. Jon Snow was a King from the House Baratheon. It was the Autumnal Equinox in The Twins when Petyr Baelish threatened the  castle of Jon Snow . Jon Snow was scared of the slowing Time power of Petyr Baelish and refused to fight back. It was the first day of Spring in Oldstones when Jon Snow met Robert Baratheon .  From Robert Baratheon Jon Snow learnt the power of teleportation.
